HEADWORD: Wadset
<hw>Wad"set</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Scot. <ets>wad</ets>
a pledge; akin to Sw. <ets>vad</ets> a wager. See <er>Wed</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Scots Law)</fld> <def>A kind of pledge or mortgage.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>wadsett</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
